verbose_text: WIN-55 inhibited TNF-alpha-induced p38 MAPK activity as well as TNF-alpha-induced increase of mRNA stability and expression / activity of nNOS; the inhibitory effect of WIN-55 was blocked by a selective CB2 antagonist.
